# 🔐 What is an IPS?

An **Intrusion Prevention System (IPS)** is a network security tool that monitors network traffic and automatically **detects and blocks malicious activities**.

| IDS              | IPS                        |
| ---------------- | -------------------------- |
| Detects attacks  | Detects + Blocks attacks   |
| Generates alerts | Prevents malicious traffic |

Snort can operate in **both IDS and IPS modes**.

